Subject: [PATCH] feat(v2.3.0): persistent agent state + portfolio P&L tracking
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Roadmap v2.3 — Persistence layer using better-sqlite3.

New module — server/persistence.js (455 lines):
- 4 tables: agents, trades, pnl_snapshots, positions
- Schema versioning (schema_version table) for future migrations
- WAL mode + NORMAL synchronous for speed without sacrificing durability
- Prepared statements cached at init for tight hot-path performance
- Downsampled P&L history queries (1min/10min/1hr buckets for 7d/30d/90d)
- Nightly retention: 90 days of snapshots, 10k most recent trades
- Graceful no-op fallback if better-sqlite3 native binding fails to load

AgentManager integration:
- saveAgent() called on every broadcastState() — state survives crash
- deleteAgent() called on kill
- On boot: loadAgents() rehydrates all non-STOPPED agents from disk,
  restoring remaining budget, trade count, P&L, last action, created_at.
  PAUSED agents stay paused; RUNNING agents restart their timer.
- Falls back to the two starter agents only when DB is empty (first boot)

Server integration (server/index.js):
- persistence.init() runs FIRST in the boot handler, before AgentManager's
  deferred rehydration timer fires, so loadAgents() has data to return
- global.recordTrade() now writes to SQLite in addition to state.trades
- New 60s interval samples total_balance / realized_pnl / open_positions /
  active_agents into pnl_snapshots table
- New hourly interval sweeps old data at ~3am local time
- Clean SIGINT/SIGTERM handlers close the DB so WAL checkpoints complete

New REST endpoints:
- GET /api/pnl/history?range=7d|30d|90d — downsampled series for charting
- GET /api/pnl/stats — {enabled, dbPath, agents, trades, snapshots, positions}

New terminal commands:
- pnl [7d|30d|90d] — summary of P&L change over range
- persist — persistence layer diagnostics

Frontend (frontend/index.html):
- New PORTFOLIO P&L section in col-3 between PREDICTIONS and TRADE FEED
- 7D/30D/90D range toggle buttons (cyan-highlighted active state)
- Hand-rolled canvas line chart (no Chart.js dep — 70KB saved)
- Color flips green/red based on sign of total delta
- Empty state for first 60s while snapshot sampler warms up
- Section header shows $ delta and % change
- Auto-refresh every 60s (matches server sampler cadence)
- Resize listener redraws on window resize

Version bumps to v2.3 across server banner, terminal help+status,
frontend header, terminal output, and footer.

Data lives at $HOME/.agentic-claw/agentic-claw.db (override with
AGENTIC_CLAW_DATA env var).
